@startuml sequence_dryrun
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Dry-Run Mode - No Rollback Needed

actor User
participant "ScaffoldCommand" as CMD
participant "IScaffoldEngine" as SE
participant "DryRunCommandService" as DRY

User -> CMD: HandleAsync(config, output, dryRun=true)

CMD -> SE: ScaffoldAsync(yaml, output, dryRun=true, force)
SE -> DRY: All writes intercepted
DRY -> DRY: Record planned files\n(nothing written to disk)
SE --> CMD: ScaffoldResult with PlannedFiles

CMD -> CMD: Log planned files
CMD --> User: "Dry run - files that would be created:\n  Create: src/Program.cs\n  Create: src/MyApp.csproj"

note right of CMD: No rollback service\nresolved or needed

@enduml
